<h2 id="hooking-up-the-logic-no-magic-yet">Hooking up the Logic: No Magic Yet <a class="headerlink" href="class-constants#hooking-up-the-logic-no-magic-yet" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>Let's add that! Open <code>BattleManager</code> and find <code>battle()</code>. Give this a new
fifth argument: <code>$battleType</code>:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="fbbe77a95f">
    <div class="meta">
        <div class="actions">
