<p>Awesome! Now, there's just <em>one</em> little last detail: if two ships are fighting in
<code>only_jedi</code> mode, and both have <em>zero</em> Jedi powers, they'll get caught in this loop
and fight forever! To prevent that, above the <code>while</code>, add a new <code>$i = 0</code> variable:</p>
