</p>
<p>Done!</p>
<p>Give it a try!. Select one Jedi Starfighter, one CloakShape fighter, and choose
"Only Jedi Powers". Hit engage and ... the Jedi Starfighter used its Jedi powers
for a stunning victory! If we refresh, one of the ships will use its Jedi powers
<em>every</em> single time.</p>
<h2 id="magic-strings-make-kittens-cry">Magic Strings Make Kittens Cry <a class="headerlink" href="class-constants#magic-strings-make-kittens-cry" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>Feature complete! And it was easy. So... what's the problem? Look at these strings:
<code>normal</code>, <code>no_jedi</code> and <code>only_jedi</code>:</p>
