</p>
<p>That will work the <em>exact</em> same way as before. In <code>index.php</code>, do the same thing:
<code>&lt;?php echo BattleManager::TYPE_NORMAL</code>. Copy that and replace it with <code>TYPE_NO_JEDI</code>
and <code>TYPE_ONLY_JEDI</code>:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="2d18d40938">
